    public class RailcarState
extends RailcarStateHbr
implements Auditable
    The RailcarState is an Operator scoped entity building on top of the entityset scoped railcar. It includes information for a railcar that is operator specific, like damage informat, last departure date, last pinconfiguration, etc.
